snippet.title: Overcooked! All You Can Eat - Swedish Chef Enters the Kitchen!
snippet.description:
Swedish Chef enters the kitchen! Get ready for even more cooking chaos as Swedish Chef is available to download now for free for all Overcooked! All You Can Eat players. 

Overcooked! All You Can Eat is available now for Xbox Series X|S.
